## When to sync

After features/fixes are merged in **this** (private) repo and you want the OSS mirror updated:

```bash
node scripts/sync-web-monitor-oss.js
```

The script:

1. Clones this repo to `../web_monitor-oss-staging` (does not alter private working tree)
2. Runs `scripts/oss-desensitize.js` (production IP/domain/WeChat AppID ŌåÆ placeholders)
3. Applies `templates/oss/.cursor/rules/` into the OSS tree
4. Commits and pushes to `https://github.com/securityWatch/web_monitor.git`

